query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('.net-4.5',
'android-manifest',
'android-volley',
'asp.net-core-2.0',
'coffeescript',
'cucumber',
'google-plus',
'histogram',
'linear-algebra',
'smtp',
'threadpool',
'tinymce',
'treeview');
